JAC Motors to Build Car Factory in Brazil

-- B y   R o b i n   S t r i n g e r
-- 
2011-08-01T19:32:22Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-01/jac-motors-to-build-car-factory-in-brazil.html
Chinese automaker Anhui Jianghuai
Automobile Co.’s Brazilian unit, JAC Motors Brasil, plans to
build a car factory in  Brazil , the company said on its Facebook
page.  Jianghuai’s plant may be ready in about two years, the
Valor Economico newspaper said earlier today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Robin Stringer in Sao Paulo at 
 rstringer@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
